eNCA's Heidi Giokos has more details. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Gauteng police commissioner, Elias Mawela and his SAPS team have descended on Vanderbijlpark,Gauteng. It is part of O Kae Molao operations aimed at cracking down on crime and lawlessness. Police have been conducting roadblocks in the area. eNCA's Heidi Giokos has more details in the video above.